flowchart LR
    IN[Inbound request] --> RL[Rate Limiting]
    RL --> HEL[Helmet headers]
    HEL --> VAL[Input Validation]
    VAL --> CTL[Thin Controller]
    CTL --> SVC[Service Layer Logic]
    SVC --> DB[(Database)]

    HUB[Hubtel callback] --> SIG[Signature Verification]
    SIG --> VAL

    ADM[Admin action] --> JWT[JWT in HttpOnly cookie]
    JWT --> CSRF[CSRF validation]
    CSRF --> CTL

    SVC --> AUD[Audit log sensitive action]
    AUD --> DB

    CODE[Delivery code] --> HASH[Hash before persistence]
    HASH --> DB
